@node "Document_5" " Programme summary"
 Programme summary

On start-up DER_PROZESS_2.0 opens a Multiscan Productivity screen which
(still) cannot be altered in any way, for this is a construction requirement
and an AGA-Amiga is necessary.

Before you indiscriminately start manipulating all the possible  levers  and
switches  etc.  or certain menu points in an inpatient manner, it is advised
that a rough scrutin be carried out for the general course of the programme.

Generally you can separate the course of the programme in the following
5 steps.


Step 1:    The sketchmodus "build"

With this mode you may, at free will, sketch your flow-sheet on the screen.


Step 2:    The testmodus "test"

Perhaps you have already discovered that with  your  know  already  sketched
flow-sheet  certain  calculations  and  functions can be done, but you must,
whether it suits you or not, test this flow-sheet by the programme.


Step 3:    The data feed mode "data"

In this mode you may feed, see and correct all the data of your flow-sheet
which you have knowledge of or wish to know.


Step 4:    The calculation mode "calc"

Starts with the calculation of in the data mode feeded data.


Step 5:    The action mode "action"

With this mode you have the possibility to simulate your tested and with
data feeded flow-sheet on the screen.


Now have fun with use of DER_PROZESS_2.0.
@endnode

